name: tp5_211231_LinesFlower
description:
t=0
draw=_=>{t||createCanvas(W=720,W)
t+=.01
colorMode(HSB)
B=blendMode
B(BLEND)
background(F=.5,.03)
B(ADD)
for(r=0;r<TAU+!(X=Y=360)+!F++;r+=.175)for(i=0;i<40;i++)stroke((i*9+r*99)%360,90,W,.5)+line(X,Y,X+=cos(R=r+noise(i/9-t)*(F%6-3)*i/9)*(L=i),Y+=sin(R)*L)}

// ref. https://twitter.com/Hau_kun/status/1476843195070021632
